Set Up

Install gradience(from flat hub) and change the background. After saving it will create an entry in .confgi/gtk4.0 and confgi/gtk3.0.
To reflect the changes for gtk3 applications install adw-gtk3-theme using the below command: 
	sudo dnf install adw-gtk3-theme

To edit gnome-shell.css create folder inside .themes/custome-theme/gnome-shell

